## 5. Workflow Completion Checklists

**After dev-story**: 更新 Story file list + Story 狀態 (`review`) + sprint-status.yaml + tracking file

**After code-review**: 建立 CR report + 更新 Story 狀態 (`done`) + sprint-status.yaml + archive tracking

**After create-story**: 建立 Story file + tracking file + 更新 sprint-status.yaml (`ready-for-dev`)

